(188, 'product_main_description', '<p>In today`s fast-paced world, managing finances can often feel like navigating a labyrinth. However, with the Dash SaaS Budget Planner, financial clarity and control are within reach. This powerful tool empowers users to efficiently track income, manage expenses, and achieve their financial goals with ease. Whether you`re a seasoned investor or a budgeting novice, our platform provides the tools and insights needed to take charge of your financial future.</p>', 'BudgetPlanner', '2024-12-07 09:08:53', '2024-12-07 09:08:53'),
