(280, 'product_main_description', '<p>Experience seamless deliveries with the Courier Management System in Dash SaaS. This dedicated tool ensures efficient order processing, real-time parcel tracking, and provides strategic insights through robust reporting features. Elevate your courier management capabilities with this comprehensive system.\n        </p>', 'CourierManagement', '2024-12-07 09:19:23', '2024-12-07 09:19:23'),
