(326, 'product_main_description', '<p>The Facilities Module in Dash SaaS is designed to enhance and streamline resource management for businesses of all sizes. This powerful tool provides a centralized platform for managing various facilities-related tasks, ensuring efficient use of resources and optimal operational performance. Whether you\'re managing office spaces, equipment, or other assets, the Facilities Module offers a comprehensive solution to simplify and automate these processes.</p>', 'Facilities', '2024-12-07 09:19:46', '2024-12-07 09:19:46'),
