(372, 'product_main_description', '<p>An Inventory management module, often found in business software systems like Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) or Inventory Management Software, typically includes a set of features and functionalities designed to handle various aspects of inventory control and optimization.</p>', 'Inventory', '2024-12-07 09:19:56', '2024-12-07 09:19:56'),
