(602, 'product_main_description', '<p>The Dash SaaS SWOT Analysis Module empowers businesses with a structured framework to evaluate their Strengths, Weaknesses, Opportunities, and Threats. This powerful tool is designed to provide clear insights into your organizations internal and external factors, helping you make informed strategic decisions.</p>', 'SWOTAnalysisModel', '2024-12-07 09:22:23', '2024-12-07 09:22:23'),
