(697, 'dedicated_theme_heading', 'Effortless Management of Challenges and Charters', 'Planning', '2024-12-07 10:19:30', '2024-12-07 10:19:30'),
(698, 'dedicated_theme_description', '<p>The Planning Module of Dash SaaS offers a centralized hub for efficiently managing challenges and charters. Gone are the days of juggling multiple documents and struggling to keep track of progress. With the Planning Module, you can easily create, update, and monitor your challenges and charters in one intuitive platform. From defining objectives to tracking milestones, our module empowers you to stay organized and focused on achieving your goals.\n        </p>', 'Planning', '2024-12-07 10:19:30', '2024-12-07 10:19:30');
