(855, 'product_main_description', '<p>An internal knowledge base is a company-made resource consisting of process documents and tools that members of the organization need to do their jobs properly. Its purpose is to mitigate organizational, technical, and learning difficulties often faced within companies that limit productivity.</p>', 'Internalknowledge', '2024-12-10 08:25:29', '2024-12-10 08:25:29'),
