(924, 'product_main_description', '<p>The Requests Module simplifies the process of making your forms accessible. Once you have designed your custom form using the user-friendly interface, just click Publish. The module will generate a shareable link or embed code, making it easy to integrate into your website or application. This ensures your form is instantly available to users, allowing you to gather important data, feedback, or inquiries effortlessly. The Requests Module streamlines the sharing and implementation of your forms, making it quick and straightforward.</p>', 'Requests', '2024-12-10 08:25:49', '2024-12-10 08:25:49'),
